(1243,	1,	'2021-02-06 16:43:01',	'2021-02-06 05:43:01',	'[et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" _builder_version=\"4.0.6\"][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.7.7\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" _builder_version=\"4.0.6\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.7.7\" custom_padding=\"0px|||||\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\"]<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #167d7f;\"><strong>The Elemental Diet and SIBO Treatment<br /></strong></span></h1>\n<h3> </h3>\n<h2> </h2>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>What is the Elemental Diet?</strong></h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The fastest, and perhaps the most effective treatment for SIBO is following a strict elemental diet for 14 - 21 days.</p>\n<p>The elemental diet is a powdered formula you mix in water which replaces your normal meals.</p>\n<p>The formula provides all the essential nutrients humans need to live broken down into their simplest forms to make them  easily and rapidly absorbed. For protein you have individual amino acids, for carbohydrates fast absorbing simple sugars like dextrose, for fat MCT powder from coconut oil, and then your essential vitamins and minerals.</p>\n<p>For 14 - 21 days the shakes are the only ‘food’ you ingest.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> </span></em></p>\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" _builder_version=\"4.0.6\" background_color=\"#0C1446\" min_height=\"736px\" custom_margin=\"8px||-12px|||\" custom_padding=\"0px||0px||false|false\" global_module=\"703\" saved_tabs=\"all\" collapsed=\"off\"][et_pb_row column_structure=\"1_2,1_2\" use_custom_gutter=\"on\" gutter_width=\"1\" module_id=\"second-sec-inner\" _builder_version=\"4.0.6\" width=\"60%\" width_tablet=\"\" width_phone=\"\" width_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" custom_padding=\"0px||0px||false|false\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"3.29.3\"][et_pb_image src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2020/