bal medicines, nutritional supplements, and eating plan.\r\n\r\nYou are given all the support you need, from recipes and eating plans, to troubleshooting, diet customisation, ongoing consultations and email support. We are there for you until the causes of your symptoms are resolved and you are living life symptom free.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" module_class=\"price-sec-one price-sec\" _builder_version=\"4.0.6\" background_color=\"#167D7F\"][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.0.6\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" _builder_version=\"4.0.6\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.0.6\" header_2_font=\"|700|||||||\" header_2_text_align=\"center\" header_2_text_color=\"#fff\" header_2_font_size=\"33px\" header_2_line_height=\"45px\"]\r\n<h2>Initial 60 Minute Consultation $200</h2>\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.0.6\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" _builder_version=\"4.0.6\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.0.6\" text_text_color=\"#ffffff\" text_font_size=\"16px\" text_line_height=\"26px\"]\r\n\r\nDuring your initial 60-minute consultation, you will sit down with your practitioner to go over your health history, and review all your symptoms and diet. This comprehensive appraisal ensures that I have all of the information needed to gain a complete understanding of all the factors affecting your health and to get a baseline from which we can track improvement in your symptoms.\r\n\r\nOn completion of your assessment, your practitioner will:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Tick0.png\" />Recommend initial functional testing such as SIBO Breath Test and Comprehensive Stool Analysis.</li>\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Tick0.png\" />Provide you with dietary guidelines, including an allowable food list, eating plan, meal plan, meal planner and recipe book.</li>\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Tick0.png\" />Recommend initial supplements and lifestyle changes for you to begin.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOnce you complete your labs and we have received the lab results you will move on to Step Two: the Report of Findings. This typically occurs 4 weeks after the Initial Consultation. While you wait for your labs to come back, you will be implementing the Eating Plan and initial supplement and lifestyle recommendations, and making forward progress\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" module_class=\"price-sec-two price-sec\" _builder_version=\"4.0.6\" background_color=\"#005437\"][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.0.6\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" _builder_version=\"4.0.6\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.0.6\" header_2_font=\"|700|||||||\" header_2_text_align=\"center\" header_2_text_color=\"#ffffff\" header_2_font_size=\"33px\" header_2_line_height=\"45px\"]\r\n<h2>Second Consultation Report of Findings 30 minutes $100</h2>\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.0.6\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" _builder_version=\"4.0.6\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.0.6\" text_text_color=\"#ffffff\" text_font_size=\"16px\" text_line_height=\"26px\" custom_padding=\"||15px||false|false\"]\r\n\r\nAt the Report of Findings visit, your Naturopath will:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Tick0.png\" />Review the results of your lab testing.</li>\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Tick0.png\" />Discuss the underlying patterns and triggers that are contributing to your symptoms.</li>\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Tick0.png\" />Outline the suggested treatment plan, including dietary, supplement and lifestyle recommendations</li>\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Tick0.png\" />Discuss the results of the Eating Plan.</li>\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Tick0.png\" />Answer any questions you have about the findings or the treatment plan.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nDepending on the findings of your test results, treatment generally follows these stages:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Tick0.png\" />Removing any abnormal growth of bacteria, yeasts and/or parasites in your gut.</li>\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Tick0.png\" />Reducing inflammation and repairing the lining of your gastrointestinal tract.</li>\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Tick0.png\" />Restoring beneficial bacteria and re-establishing healthy bacterial balance in your gut</li>\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Tick0.png\" />Restoring digestive secretions and gut immunity.</li>\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Tick0.png\" />Identifying food intolerances</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" module_class=\"price-sec-thr price-sec\" _builder_version=\"4.0.6\" background_color=\"#167d7f\"][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.0.6\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" _builder_version=\"4.0.6\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.0.6\" header_2_font=\"|700|||||||\" header_2_text_align=\"center\" header_2_text_color=\"#ffffff\" header_2_font_size=\"33px\" header_2_line_height=\"45px\"]\r\n<h2>Follow up Consultations 30 minute $100</h2>\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.0.6\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" _builder_version=\"4.0.6\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.0.6\" text_text_color=\"#ffffff\" text_font_size=\"16px\" text_line_height=\"26px\" custom_padding=\"||15px||false|false\"]\r\n\r\nOnce the Case Review is complete, you’ll have follow-up appointments every 4 weeks to check in with your progress as you move through the different stages of treatment At these visits, we will:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Tick0.png\" />review your progress on the treatment plan,</li>\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Tick0.png\" />fine-tune your protocol,</li>\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Tick0.png\" />troubleshoot any issues,</li>\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Tick0.png\" />customise your eating plan and reintroduce foods,</li>\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Tick0.png\" />make additional recommendations, and answer any questions you may have</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" module_class=\"regular-check\" _builder_version=\"4.0.6\"][et_pb_row column_structure=\"1_2,1_2\" use_custom_gutter=\"on\" gutter_width=\"2\" _builder_version=\"4.0.6\" width=\"70%\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.0.6\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.0.6\" text_font_size=\"16px\" header_2_font=\"Raleway|600|||||||\" header_2_text_align=\"center\" header_2_text_color=\"#157c7d\" header_2_font_size=\"29px\" text_orientation=\"center\"]\r\n<h2>Regular email check ins</h2>\r\nYour practitioner will email you to monitor your progress and answer any questions you may have.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.0.6\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.0.6\" text_font_size=\"16px\" header_2_font=\"Raleway|600|||||||\" header_2_text_align=\"center\" header_2_text_color=\"#157c7d\" header_2_font_size=\"29px\" text_orientation=\"center\"]\r\n<h2>Unlimited email support</h2>\r\nOngoing guidance, motivation and support through unlimited email support: get your questions answered as they arise, so you always have clarity about the treatment plan\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" _builder_version=\"4.0.6\" background_color=\"#0C1446\" min_height=\"736px\" custom_margin=\"8px||-12px|||\" custom_padding=\"0px||0px||false|false\" global_module=\"703\" saved_tabs=\"all\" collapsed=\"off\"][et_pb_row column_structure=\"1_2,1_2\" use_custom_gutter=\"on\" gutter_width=\"1\" module_id=\"second-sec-inner\" _builder_version=\"4.0.6\" width=\"60%\" width_tablet=\"\" width_phone=\"\" width_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" custom_padding=\"0px||0px||false|false\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"3.29.3\"][et_pb_image src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/tablet0-2-1.png\" align=\"center\" _builder_version=\"4.0.6\" width=\"66%\" custom_margin=\"||0px||false|false\"][/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.0.6\" custom_padding=\"20px||||false|false\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.0.6\" text_font_size=\"16px\" header_2_font=\"Raleway|700|||||||\" header_2_text_color=\"#ffffff\" header_2_font_size=\"25px\" header_2_line_height=\"1.3em\" custom_margin=\"-22px||||false|false\" custom_padding=\"0px||8px||false|false\"]\r\n<h2>Download the Free Guide and discover:</h2>\r\n<ul class=\"list\">\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Tick0.png\" />The latest research on the causes of IBS.</li>\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Tick0.png\" />Which foods you should be avoiding (for now).</li>\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Tick0.png\" />Which tests can help you identify the cause of your symptoms.</li>\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Tick0.png\" />Easy tips for better digestion.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.0.6\" custom_m