mme you are committing to this process, with the understanding that it takes time and work to become symptom free, this makes success more probable.</li>\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/tick-blue.png\" />You are accountable to someone, this keeps you engaged and on track.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.0.6\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.0.6\" text_text_color=\"#9b9b9b\" header_2_font=\"|600|||||||\" header_2_text_color=\"#4a4a4a\" header_2_font_size=\"32px\" header_2_line_height=\"52px\"]\r\n<h2>Who is this programme for?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/tick-blue.png\" />You have been suffering with digestive issues, bloating, gas, pain, diarrhea, constipation, reflux, etc. for a number of years.</li>\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/tick-blue.png\" />You want to discover and correct the root cause of your symptoms, rather than just suppressing them.</li>\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/tick-blue.png\" />You understand that getting better is a process that requires time and effort.</li>\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/tick-blue.png\" />You are prepared to make the diet and lifestyle changes needed to help achieve this.</li>\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/tick-blue.png\" />You understand the value of being supported and guided through this process.</li>\r\n 	<li><img src=\"http://digestivewellness.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/tick-blue.png\" />You are ready for a change and highly motivated to be free of your symptoms for good.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" module_class=\"what-nxt\" _builder_version=\"4.0.6\" background_color=\"#EBF5F7\"][et_p